the late palestinian leader arafat 's cabinet secretary abu delman disclosed that arafat was poisoned by people when he received a delegation of supporters at the headquarters in ramallah a year ago .
" about a year ago , a strange thing happened to arafat , which was on september 25 , 2003 , " abu dhabi told the al - qaeda daily .
at that time , the chairman shook hands with about 30 support representatives one by one , and after that , the chairman had a vomiting phenomenon .
since then , the president 's health has gradually worsened . "
arafat died of unknown disease at the french hospital on november 11 .
some high - level palestinian officials believe that arafat is being poisoned by people .
however , doctors in france said that the allegation was groundless .
two weeks ago , israeli prime minister sharon 's cabinet made a decision to drive arafat out of office , but did not say what means to use .
israel 's threat has triggered a wave of support from the world for arafat , and arafat has met with several groups of supporters .
abu delman recalled , " arafat shook hands with these people , and they came to express their support to arafat , who was besieged by israel . "
on 25 september last year , arafat met with two groups , one from the world and the other from the group of free cyclists who advocate peace , and the other from the political movement .
