speaking at a year - end press conference in the kremlin , putin said that " russia is now using an absolute legal market mechanism to protect its national interests . "
i think this is completely normal . "
russian state - owned oil companies today became the new east of the company after purchasing the bekal financial group of the company , which had previously been listed in the secret auction .
the russian state - owned oil company suddenly announced early last night that it had obtained 100 percent of the shares of the unknown bekal financial group .
the acquisition has enabled the kremlin to firmly control russia 's important energy industry .
in the past 18 months , russian authorities have been attacking yukos and its founder , hundreds of millions of billionaire khodorkovsky .
russia 's state - owned oil companies are merging with russia 's state - owned gas companies , and the company will control one - fifth of russia 's total oil production and all natural gas production and become the world 's largest energy group at one stroke .
putin defended the state 's current acquisition by attacking the privatization black box operation in the 1990 s .
