according to statistics , the death toll has climbed to nearly 150,000 .
the relief supplies of the governments of various countries have continued , and us president bush has entrusted his father , the elder bush , and former president clinton , to be responsible for raising donations from the public .
the delegation led by us secretary of state powell arrived in thailand last night to express us concern and assess the progress of the rescue work before the crisis summit in the indonesian capital of jakarta on the 6 th .
