hiv carriers in beijing increase by 40 percent
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 1 ( reporters zhao xinpei and li xu ) the beijing municipal health bureau recently announced the latest figures of hiv - infected people in beijing : from 1985 to october 2004 , beijing municipality has reported a total of 2,046 cases of hiv - infected people , with an average annual increase of 40.6 percent .
according to national aids statistics , beijing municipality ranks eighth in the country in terms of the number of hiv carriers .
of the 2,046 cases of hiv carriers , 403 were residents in beijing , 1,507 were floating population from elsewhere , 106 were foreigners , and 30 were unaccounted for .
according to analysis , the hiv infection in beijing municipality is mainly caused by the use of static drugs and the spread of sex , and the hiv infection of the floating population is mainly through the use of static drugs and the use of blood for blood , and the hiv infection of foreign personnel is mainly caused by sexual transmission .
in order to prevent the further spread of aids , starting from july 2004 , the disease prevention and control centers of 18 districts and counties in beijing municipality have set up free consultation rooms and antibodies screening laboratories to conduct face - to - face consultation , initial blood screening , epidemiological investigation , and gradually spread to hospitals at and above the city level .
the beijing municipal health bureau has designated the geotan hospital and the youan hospital as a designated hospital for the free treatment of aids in beijing municipality . the clinical part of the work of free treatment of aids is to be purchased by the beijing municipal health bureau and the unified organization of the municipal financial bureau .
the beijing municipal education commission has studied and formulated a free teaching policy for hiv - infected people and children , as well as a policy for the study of aids patients among young students .
at present , hospitals at and above the level of the obstetrics and gynaecology department in the whole city are undertaking free consultation and screening of aids , and the prefectural hospital and youan hospital are providing anti - viral drug hospitals for pregnant women .
at present , a total of 1,390 automatic sales machines have been installed at the district level free of charge , and a pilot scheme for methadone treatment and the establishment of a clean needle - sharing point for drug abusers has been carried out .
