xinhua news agency , shanghai , december 1 ( reporter jiang wei ) with the completion of the trial operation of a 660,000 - kilowatts power generating unit , the shanghai electric power station group company , ltd. , on the 1 st completed the production target of 15 - million kilowatts per year ahead of schedule , with the result that the output and production capacity of the shanghai power station has risen to the first place in the world , realizing the long - cherished wish of several generations of people in china 's equipment manufacturing industry .
the shanghai electric power plant group is china 's largest power station equipment manufacturing base .
in recent years , due to the rapid growth of demand for power generation equipment in china , the power generation manufacturers throughout the country have entered a stage of high growth and large - scale development .
the shanghai electric power station group has integrated the superior resources of the equipment of the power stations , such as the engine , the boilers of the power station , and so on . after receiving four 1 - million kilowatt - class thermal power generating units , it has also obtained the production orders for nine heavy gas power generating units and three remaining thermal boilers in the form of an overall tender .
at the same time , through integrated operations , we have further enhanced the efficiency of enterprise management , technological development , and production .
at present , the shanghai electric power station group has accounted for 40 percent of the market share of the equipment industry of china 's power stations , and has constantly expanded its overseas markets in the middle east , southeast asia , and south america .
in the first year of this year alone , as the main components of power generation equipment , the shanghai automotive machinery company received a sales order worth 6 billion yuan .
zheng jianhua , president of the shanghai electric power station group , said : the " power shortage " this summer has greatly increased the demand for power stations and equipment in all parts of the country , and the competition in the manufacturing market for power stations ' equipment has become increasingly hot .
the group is implementing the three major goals of " developing and manufacturing 1 million kilowatts of thermal power , gas generating units , and 1 million kilowatts of nuclear power , " so as to achieve the goal of becoming the world 's 500 largest .
( hong kong , macau , taiwan ) hong kong observatory provides new services to wmo website
xinhua news agency , hong kong , december 2 , the hong kong observatory started to provide two new services for the " world weather information service " and the " bad weather information center " websites managed by the world meteorological organization ( wmo ) from the 2 nd .
a spokesman for the hong kong observatory said that the two new services are : the inclusion of official global weather observation on cloud volume and rainfall on the " world weather information service " website , and the revision of tropical cyclone mobile path in the past seven days on the " bad weather information center " website .
these two services are another new service provided by the hong kong observatory to the " severe weather information center " at the beginning of this year , following the official observation of heavy rain ( including heavy snow ) around the world .
it has been learned that the " world weather information service " website has always provided official weather forecasts for major cities in the world and the average monthly climate of cities .
the new service is the first of its kind in the world to provide official weather observations and a global distribution map of cloud and rainfall .
the new website covers a wide range of weather observations , high density and is updated eight times a day .
the new product of the " bad weather information center " website is the revisiting function of providing tropical cyclone mobile paths .
in the past , the website had no longer kept information on the location of the tropical cyclone when the tropical cyclone was dispersed .
however , a few days after the tropical cyclone landed , the public still wanted to obtain relevant information on the tropical cyclone .
for this reason , the new product has stored the tropical cyclone grading , location and mobile path for the past seven days , so that the public and the media can still obtain the necessary information in a few days after the tropical cyclone landed and dispersed .
the world 's first bird flu virus hatch 5nik - 1 rapid diagnosis drug testing box successfully developed in shantou
xinhua news agency , shantou , december 3 ( zhang wenwen and lin junqiang ) - the reporter learned from the shantou university medical school and the joint flu research center of the university of hong kong that they have cooperated with xiamen university in the past half a year to develop the world 's first case of the rapid diagnosis drug box of the avian flu virus , and the first of its kind in the world .
using this fast testing method to test the samples of suspected people can reach a conclusion within an hour as soon as possible on whether or not to be infected with the avian flu virus .
according to professor guan tie , director of the joint flu research center of the faculty of medicine of shantou university and the faculty of medicine of the university of hong kong , according to the information currently available , the mortality rate of avian flu , which is listed as a highly toxic and deadly virus , is far higher than the salts virus .
in the past , it took more than one week for the virus to go from " suspected " to " confirmed " for three to five days .
the rapid testing technology for the avian flu virus , which has been successfully introduced this time , has adopted the method of enzyme , the method of immunity , and the method of gold standards , which can test the complete virus or the virus of the virus , which includes the excretion of the mouth , and the cultivation of the chickens , as well as the blood , and will be able to reach a conclusion in one hour and two hours at the earliest .
the new technology has the characteristics of being simple , convenient , and quick , and can be tested on the spot in the epidemic areas , and the accuracy rate is more than 90 percent , which is conducive to early detection , early diagnosis , early isolation , and early treatment of the virus , and to preventing the spread of the virus on a large scale and causing great disasters .
entrusted by the china disease prevention and control center , the shantou university 's medical school and the joint flu research center of the university of hong kong recently held a training course on bird flu virus testing technology to train the students from the disease prevention and control centers of 20 provinces and cities across the country , including the latest avian flu virus rapid testing technology .
