the participants fully expressed their views on the international and domestic economic trends , consolidating the results of macroeconomic regulation and control , further strengthening agriculture , deepening the reform of state - owned enterprises , developing the non-public economy , improving financial services , preventing financial risks , expanding employment , improving the social security system , and maintaining the basic stability of prices .
wen jiabao and other leading comrades of the state council seriously listened to their speeches and discussed with them .
after listening to their speeches , wen jiabao said : you have put forward many good opinions and suggestions , and the state council will absorb and adopt them when studying economic work .
he stressed : to implement the spirit of the fourth plenary session of the 16 th cpc central committee , an important task is to further improve the decision - making mechanism and implement scientific and democratic decision - making .
this is an important measure to enhance the party 's ruling ability and the government 's administrative ability .
with regard to major policy decisions concerning the overall situation of economic and social development , the government should conduct in - depth investigation and study through various channels and forms , grasp the actual situation , and extensively concentrate the wisdom of the people , so that the decision - making can truly be based on science and democracy .
wu yi , zeng peiyan , hui liangyu , hua jianmin , and other leading comrades of the state council , as well as responsible persons of relevant departments , attended the forum .
( international ) angolan president 's council holds special meeting in peru
xinhua news agency , kustko , peru , december 7 ( reporter liu guoqiang and wang lu ) the special meeting of the president 's council of the andes community ( the andes ) opened on the 7 th in the famous tourist city of kustko , peru .
the presidents or representatives attending the meeting will hold consultations on deepening the andes regional integration plan and promoting economic and social development .
speaking at the opening ceremony of the meeting , peruvian president toledo toledo said that it has been 35 years since the founding of the andes , but some major problems such as poverty have not been solved .
at present , the poverty rate in the andes region is as high as 53 percent , which constitutes a serious threat to the democratic administration in the region .
to this end , the governments of the region should work hard to explore ways to establish an effective mechanism for extricating themselves from poverty and strengthen their participation in state affairs so as to promote social stability and development .
the south american community will announce the establishment of the third south american summit , which is scheduled to be held here today .
he expressed the belief that the establishment of this new regional organization will play an important role in promoting regional political , economic , and social development .
apart from toledo , bolivian president mesa also attended the meeting .
colombian president ricardo lagos , ecuador 's president gutierres , and venezuelan president chavez were unable to attend the meeting for various reasons . however , they will come to attend the third south american summit here on 8 june .
the andes community was founded in 1969 and is composed of five countries , namely bolivia , colombia , ecuador , venezuela , and peru . it is a regional organization for economic cooperation among latin american countries , with its headquarters in the peruvian capital lima .
the president 's council is the highest decision - making body in the region .
the last meeting was held in the capital of ecuador in july 2003 .
construction of three gorges power station to start soon
xinhua news agency , wuhan , december 8 ( reporter shi yongfeng ) on december 8 , the main body of the three gorges project 's underground power station was open for bidding for the first time , thus opening the prelude to the construction of the three gorges underground power station .
the three gorges project is designed and installed with 26 generating units of 700,000 kilowatts , with an installed capacity of 18.2 million kilowatts , with an annual average power generation of 84.7 billion kilowatt - hours after all the units have been put into production .
in order to further tap the power generation potential of the three gorges project , the three gorges project has set aside the position of expanding the underground power station in its initial design .
according to a briefing given by a responsible person of the china three gorges project development corporation , the three gorges underground power station is located in the mountains on the right side of the three gorges dam . the main buildings include the water tower , the water diversion tunnel , the main plant , the tail water system , the mother line , and the 500 - kilovolts power station .
six generating units of 700,000 kilowatts will be installed at the underground power station .
this way , the total installed capacity of the three gorges project will increase from 26 to 32 , and the installed capacity will increase from 18.2 million kilowatts to 22.4 million kilowatts , greatly increasing the power generation capacity of the three gorges project .
flood prevention is the primary task of the three gorges project .
according to the plan for the operation and management of the three gorges reservoir , before the flood season every year , the water level in the three gorges reservoir will drop from the normal water level of 175 meters to the flood prevention limit of 145 meters .
therefore , the construction of underground power stations will increase the use of water in the three gorges reservoir , reduce the quantity of water to be discarded , and increase power generation , so that the power station will be able to maximize the period of water diversion .
at present , the early stage of the construction of the three gorges underground power station , such as the excavation of the tunnel , the excavation of the tail pipe , and the maintenance of the project , has begun first .
it has been learned that all underground power stations will be completed and put into production by the end of 2008 .
china 's navigation festival ready to come out
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 8 ( reporter huang fuhui ) at a news conference held here on the 8 th , yao mingde , president of the china road transportation association , expressed " full confidence " in the establishment of the china sea festival .
yao mingde , who is also director of the office of the leading group for the preparatory work for the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's fall into the sea , said that all the 16 leading groups , including the ministry of communications , have agreed to designate july 11 each year , that is , the day of zheng he 's first voyage to the west , as china 's maritime festival , and will propose to the state the establishment of this festival .
it has been learned that the state council should approve the establishment of a holiday that does not require a holiday .
zheng he is a well - known maritime family in the world .
in the 28 years from 1405 to 1433 , zheng he led more than 200 ships and nearly 30,000 people to the red sea and africa on seven occasions . he traveled more than 300,000 kilometers to more than 30 countries and regions in asia and africa through southeast asia and the indian ocean .
china will hold a series of activities next year to mark the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's voyage to the west .
the emblems of the commemorative activities were issued in beijing on the 8 th .
the logo is made up of the sailing boat , the surging light blue arc , and the words " the 600 th anniversary of the zheng he 's voyage to the west , 1405 - 2005 . "
the designer is yao ying , an art teacher at xian city middle school in shaanxi province .
people from all walks of life in society have called for seizing the opportunity of the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's voyage to the west and strengthening the education of minors in 2005 to set up china 's maritime festival , so as to enhance people 's maritime awareness and maritime concepts , carry forward the spirit of the chinese nation , and deepen the education on patriotism .
yao mingde said : china has a sea area of over 3 million square kilometers , and 90 percent of china 's international trade has been completed by sea .
china is a big sea - going country in the world , and it is not necessary to have no navigation festival in many festivals .
taiwan province has established july 11 as a maritime festival .
more than 10 countries in the world , such as the united states , canada , and japan , have a maritime festival .
( international ) cote d'ivoire reaches consensus on implementation of peace accord
xinhua news agency , abidjan , december 8 ( reporter liu shaoping ) the un action mission in cote d'ivoire issued a communique in abidjan on the evening of the 8 th , saying that un secretary general annan welcomed the consensus reached by all parties in cote d'ivoire on the continued implementation of the peace agreement , and called on all parties to seize this opportunity to ensure " true progress " in the peace process so as to prepare for the general election in october 2005 .
the communique said that annan stressed at the same time that all parties in kuwait should reach a consensus on the " concrete action plan . "
he also " placed high hopes " on south african president mbeki and the african union 's continued efforts to work together with the west african community and the un peacekeeping mission in kosovo to resolve the kosovo crisis .
entrusted by the african union , mbeki paid a four - day visit to cote d'ivoire from the 2 nd to the 6 th of this month to seek a solution to the crisis in cote d'ivoire .
at the end of the visit , mbeki announced that all parties in cote d'ivoire have reached a consensus on the four - point proposal .
the proposal includes the completion of the relevant legislation of the " markuxi agreement , " the start of the process of disarming the war personnel , and the return of all government ministers to their posts to perform their duties and restore the security of the country .
the chairman of the party group of the parliament of cote d ' ivoire recently decided that the parliament will examine the draft amendments to the constitution from the 10 th .
the opposition armed forces in cote d ' ivoire also announced today that the leaders of the opposition armed forces will hold a meeting in the near future to conduct an overall evaluation of the peace process and discuss the issue of disarming .
a coup and civil war broke out in cote d'ivoire in september 2002 .
in january last year and july this year , representatives of major political parties and opposition armed forces in cote d'ivoire reached agreements in france and ghana , agreeing to resume peace and realize national reconciliation .
however , the process of implementing the agreement has gone through twists and turns , resulting in repeated setbacks in the peace process .
in mid - october , the opposition armed forces in the northern part of cote d ' ivoire announced the recall of their representatives to participate in the government and the peace process in cote d'ivoire has been bogged down again in a deadlock .
in early november , the situation in kuwait was further worsened after a serious clash between the government forces of cote d'ivoire and the french troops in kosovo .
us $ 10 million to help children and villages in china 's western region
xinhua news agency , xi ' an , december 9 ( reporter liu ximei ) - the state director of the " international plan " , james morris , and the director of the shaanxi provincial environmental protection bureau , he fali , signed a cooperation agreement in xian on the 9 th . as of today , the international plan for china 's " water supply and environmental hygiene " project will formally cooperate with shaanxi province 's " green civilization demonstration project " to promote and help the implementation of the project of drinking water for people and animals in shaanxi province .
the " green civilization demonstration project " was initiated by shaanxi province 's environmental protection department , with a view to building green schools , green communities , green enterprises , and green villages .
after cooperating with the international plan for china 's " water supply and environmental hygiene " project , this project will promote the development of water supply and environmental hygiene in poor rural areas , as well as the construction of " green villages " and " green schools " in poverty - stricken areas , so that the two sides can complement each other 's strong points and strengthen the sustainable development of the projects .
international programmes are the world 's largest international humanitarian organization with children as the center , and more than 1.3 million children and their families and communities are directly assisted by them .
the international plan to enter china in 1995 has so far sponsored more than 21,300 children .
at present , there are six international projects in china . in addition to beijing 's yanqing county , the other five projects are located in shaanxi province ( pu cheng county , chunhua county , jiaxian county , yulin city 's yuyang district , and xixiang county ) .
since the beginning of cooperation with shaanxi province in 1999 , the total international investment in the development of poverty - stricken children and communities in more than 250 villages in shaanxi province has exceeded 12 million us dollars .
( international ) another 1,425 right - wing militants in colombia give up their arms
xinhua news agency , bogota , december 10 ( reporter liu lianxiang ) a total of 1,425 armed elements of the colombian rightwing military organization , the " joint self - defense forces of colombia , " led by deputy commander - in - chief and chief of the general staff mankuso , surrendered their weapons to the government representatives in the northeast border area on the 10th to accept the government 's arrangements for the peaceful separation .
according to reports from the media here , the people who were loyal this time belonged to the " cartagong river column , " which had previously carried out illegal armed activities in four northeastern provinces , the " joint self-defense force of colombia . "
at the ceremony , on behalf of the government , the senior peace commissioner of the colombian government , lestro , accepted their hand - handed rifles , machine guns , bombs , mortars , and other equipment , and welcomed their sincere actions .
this is the fourth time that the colombian government has dispersed 855 members of the " joint self - defense forces of colombia " since november 2003 .
in june this year , the colombian government and the " joint self - defense forces of colombia " reached a peaceful separation agreement through consultations .
the agreement stipulates that the 3,000 armed personnel of the 11 columns of the " joint self - defense forces of colombia " will be dispersed one after another and return to society by the end of this year .
the " colombian joint self-defense force , " which has nearly 20,000 people , was founded in 1997 . it is composed of the owners of the dazhuang garden , the owners of mines , and the private armed forces of drug trafficking groups .
under the mediation of the organization of american states , the organization is currently negotiating with the colombian government and has promised to send out all the personnel by the end of 2005 .
