the baise uprising was another successful armed uprising led by the independent communist party following the nanchang uprising , the autumn harvest uprising , and the guangzhou uprising .
on the morning of 11 december , more than 2,000 people , holding flowers in their hands , came to the monument to the baise uprising , presented flowers , and bow to the memory of the great achievements of the martyrs .
after that , he watched the film " baise uprising " and visited the photo exhibition " zhang yunyi in guangxi . "
