a recent survey conducted by a relevant department in shanghai municipality shows that the average number of minors reading extra - curricular books for 1.17 hours a day , 1.05 hours on television , and 0.99 hours on the internet , and about half of the time for making arrangements for the extra - school hours of minors , and the media are using a brand - new social force to become a factor that can not be ignored in the growth and development of minors .
