( international ) un warns that global drug abuse death toll will increase in 2005
xinhua news agency , vienna , december 17 ( reporter song guocheng ) - the executive director of the un drug control and crime prevention office , kosta , warned in a press release on the 17 th that due to the increase in the output of heroin in afghanistan , it is estimated that the global black market price of heroin will be stable and the grade of heroin will be raised in 2005 , resulting in the death of more drug addicts .
kosta has issued a warning to health and anti - drug officials in europe and neighboring countries , calling on them to pay attention to the latest trends of drug cultivation and international drug crimes in afghanistan and take appropriate preventive measures .
according to statistics provided by the un drug control and crime prevention office in vienna , when the opium cultivation in afghanistan was banned in 2001 , the output of heroin in afghanistan decreased by 94 percent , and the purity of heroin in the black market in europe was reduced by 50 percent in the second year .
between 2000 and 2002 , the number of drug addicts in europe decreased by 20 percent .
he said that compared with 2003 , afghanistan 's opium growing area has increased by 64 percent this year , with the output of heroin reaching more than 500 tons , which is higher than that of the black market in the world . this trend means that the global drug purity and the number of drug - related deaths have increased .
the increase in the supply of heroin on the black market means a " death sentence " for drug addicts , he said .
according to estimates , the number of deaths caused by excessive drug abuse in the world is about 100,000 a year .
( international ) us military confirms another guantanamo prisoner not an enemy fighter
xinhua news agency , washington , december 20 ( reporter pan yunzhao and tan xinmu ) at a news conference held by the pentagon on the 20th , us defense department navy secretary goden england said that a military review group has confirmed that a prisoner detained at the us navy base at guantanamo is not an enemy fighter and will be released soon .
this is the second guantanamo prisoner identified by the us military as not an enemy fighter .
england said that the pentagon confirmed the identity of the prisoner one or two days ago , and the state department will notify the country where the prisoner belongs and arrange for the release of the prisoner .
however , he did not reveal the name and nationality of the prisoner , nor did he explain the circumstances under which he was arrested .
england refused to admit that the defense department had made mistakes in determining the identity of the guantanamo prisoner .
he said that the military review team responsible for examining the identity of the guantanamo prisoner had examined 507 prisoners and confirmed the identity of 230 people , of whom 228 were enemy combat personnel .
so far , the united states has released about 200 guantanamo prisoners , some of whom have been released after being repatriated , and a small number of others have been detained after returning home , but at least 12 people have taken part in the crackdown on the us military after being released .
at present , the us navy base at guantanamo has detained about 550 " al - qaeda " and taliban suspects , most of whom were captured during the us war against afghanistan .
the us government claims that these people are enemy combat personnel , not prisoners of war , and therefore are not protected by the " geneva convention . "
many countries have criticized the us government for indefinitely detaining their citizens , and some international organizations have also criticized the us government for violating international law .
top national domain name nodes settle in shanghai
xinhua news agency , shanghai , december 21 ( feng yizhen and chen haiyu ) on the 21 st , the china internet information center and the shanghai information industry ( group ) company , ltd. signed a contract in shanghai on the top - notch national domain name nodes .
the domain name is a communications foundation for all internet applications , such as e - commerce and e - administration . at present , it is widely used as an internet address .
when people visit websites and receive and receive e - mail , they must first input their domain names , and use the domain name analysis service of the domain name system to change the domain name to the web site address , find the main computer of the website , and realize the transmission of information .
the domain name system is like a " nerve system " that controls the transmission of information on the internet .
according to mao wei , director of the china internet information center , which manages china 's top - class domain name system , up to now , china has more than 90 million internet users , ranking second in the world in terms of scale , and the number of web sites has exceeded 650,000 .
with the rapid development of the internet , the resolution of domain names has also increased rapidly .
at present , the number of cn domain names registered is increasing at a rate of 10,000 new per month , reaching 430,000 .
the top - class national domain name servers operated and managed by the china internet information center handle more than 380 million domain name analysis requests a day , with an average of over 4,400 per second , with a peak of over 8,000 .
in the face of the rapid development trend of the internet , the china internet information center , the china domain name registration management organization , has reevaluated the four top national domain name nodes in the whole country this year , and has redeployed the top cn domain name nodes according to the assessment situation .
according to the local level of internet development and the software and hardware conditions of the access units , it is decided to settle the top national domain name nodes in shanghai .
it has been learned that at present , shanghai has 45,000 cn domain names , 26.6 percent of the internet users , and the internet popularization rate and application level are ranked first in the country .
the east china region around shanghai has 130,000 cn domain names and 23,000 websites , and the level of development is also in the forefront .
for this reason , shanghai has been selected as the first nodes in the re - deployment plan .
china becomes world 's largest producer of hard alloy
xinhua news agency , nanchang , december 22 ( reporters yang zhiyuan and li xingwen ) in recent years , china 's hard - quality alloy industry has developed rapidly , with an annual output of more than one - third of the world 's hard alloy output . in terms of production scale and output , china has become the world 's largest production power with a complete variety of hard - quality alloy , and most of its products can be produced in china .
this reporter learned from the ongoing seminar on the development strategy of the ganzhou industry in china on the 22 nd .
the development of the hard - quality alloy industry is called " industrial teeth , " because it has a very high degree of hard work and endurance for the use of cutting tools , high - pressure tools , and mining and road - building machinery , and the development of the hard - quality alloy industry has played a very important role in the development of the entire industry .
it has been learned that china 's hard alloy started in the 1950 s and has been growing from nothing to nothing , and has made remarkable achievements so far .
in the early 1980 's , when the world 's annual output of hard alloy was 25,000 tons , china 's annual output of hard alloy was about 5,000 tons , and in the 21 st century , the world 's annual output of hard alloy reached 38,000 tons , while china 's output of hard alloy has rapidly increased to 15,000 tons , exceeding one - third of the world 's output of hard alloy .
china has also made marked progress in exporting hard alloy .
in 1986 , china 's annual export volume of hard alloy was only 100 tons , and by 2003 , the export volume has reached 2,500 tons , and this year 's export volume is expected to exceed 3,000 tons , which is equivalent to one - third of the world 's export volume of hard alloy , and the annual foreign exchange earned from the export of hard alloy has increased from less than $ 4 million in the past to $ 70 million per year .
adb supports shanxi 's use of coal and gas in power generation
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 23 ( reporter jiang guocheng ) the reporter learned from the asian development bank 's representative office in china on the 23 rd that the adb recently approved a loan of 174 million us dollars to support the construction of a power plant with an octane gas in the southern part of shanxi province in the process of coal mining .
the project will use the latest technology to increase the output of coal and coal fields to provide fuel for a 120,000 - kilowatt power plant .
according to the project , the project will provide at least 166 million cubic meters of coal annually to about 90,000 households and industrial and commercial users upon completion of the project in 2008 .
about 410,000 people in the jincheng area will benefit .
shanxi 's coal output accounts for about one - third of the country 's total coal output .
the total cost of the project is estimated to be 237 million us dollars , of which the bank will provide 20 million us dollars in loans , and the construction bank of china will provide 37.86 million us dollars in loans .
the city government and the two mining / industrial groups in the region will provide a total of 61.44 million u.s. dollars in capital .
the us trade development agency has also provided a grant of 500,000 us dollars for the project .
through the surface - to - surface drilling of underground coal pits , the methane obtained from the mine is called coal - level gas , and the methane generated in underground coal mining operations is called coal mine gas .
methane is an extremely explosive gas that needs to be discharged first in coal mining operations to ensure the safety of the working environment .
eliminating , collecting , and using methane will reduce greenhouse gas emissions and will help reduce global warming and climate change .
the greenhouse effect of methane is 21 times that of carbon dioxide .
the use of methane to replace coal can also increase the use of clean fuel , improve the efficiency of coal mines , and make the air more clean .
adb senior project expert hansen said that the project is expected to provide about 4.5 million tons of carbon dioxide emissions reduction .
( international ) counterfeit goods in israeli museum town hall
xinhua news agency , jerusalem , december 24 , the director of the israeli museum , james nye , said on the 24 th that the treasure of the museum 's town , ivory coast , was recently confirmed to be a fake product .
this ivory coast was once regarded as the only cultural relics that have been discovered so far in the solomon era .
in a statement , snye said that the authorities had carefully assessed the ivory coast , which was big or small .
experts found that it should be the cultural relics of the qing dynasty , which was far earlier than the first holy palace of the jews .
" the sacred palace of god , the sacred place of god , and the worship of the god . "
and these words were later verified .
in the 1980 s , the israeli museum spent us $ 550,000 on buying this ivory from an anonymous collector .
archaeological and heritage experts once believed that it was the only heritage left over from the time , as it was a treasure set by the first holy palace memorial department at the top of a stick .
snye said that before the purchase of ivory coast , experts such as the israeli archaeological community , such as naman al - aqsa , identified it as a true product .
according to a report by israel 's " land newspaper , " at that time , aghazadeh only used a large mirror to conduct a rough appraisal of the cultural relics .
this argument was denied by alwi himself .
in recent months , the israeli police have successively uncovered three large - scale cultural relics fraud cases , and have summoned hundreds of people .
in the course of investigation , the police and the cultural heritage administration unexpectedly discovered ivory coast being counterfeit .
the police will file a lawsuit against some of the suspects next week .
in the 10 th century ad , the jewish king solomon built the first holy palace on the noble rock of the present , and kept a cabinet , a ship , and other sacred things . these sacred things were destroyed later .
shenzhen to implement mandatory application of " water in water " in some buildings and small areas
xinhua news agency , guangzhou , december 26 , as a major measure to build a " water - saving " city , shenzhen will implement the application of " water - saving " in a number of relatively large buildings and small areas . at present , relevant water design standards and regulations are being formulated .
" chinese water " mainly refers to non - potable water that can be reused within a certain scope by reaching a certain amount of water quality standard after the treatment of urban sewage or domestic sewage .
the water quality is between tap water and discharge of sewage into the pipeline .
in general , a large amount of water will be used in the areas of toilet washing , garden irrigation , farmland irrigation , road maintenance , car - washing , urban spray - spraying , and cooling equipment to supplement water .
a survey conducted by the shenzhen municipal water resources department shows that in the mid - 1990s , more than 70 buildings in shenzhen city had a " water recovery " system . however , due to the impact of technical , design , and management factors , the cost of recovery and utilization of " water " was too high , and the construction units had no choice but to give up their use .
to enable these pipelines to play their role in real terms , it is only necessary to invest 300,000 to 400,000 yuan in the installation of the " water treatment system . "
if we use more than 70 sets of " middle water " pipes at present , and calculated on the basis of the 500 tons of " middle water " used in each small residential area every day , we will be able to save 35,000 tons of water for shenzhen every day .
it has been learned that the work of recovering " water from china " in shenzhen city will start with the transformation of more than 70 buildings with the original " water " recycling system , and will be further popularized after summing up experience .
at the same time , the shenzhen waterworks department will work together with the urban planning and construction departments to formulate as soon as possible the design standards for " water in the water " and stipulate that the application of " water in the water " should be mandatory in some relatively large - scale buildings .
after the treatment , the " chinese water " will be used first in urban greening and irrigation .
27 zhejiang tourists who suffered tsunamis get out of danger
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , december 27 ( reporter feng yuan , qu lingyan , hu zuohua ) - a 27 - member zhejiang tourism delegation to thailand 's puji island was safe in a life - and - death race with the tsunami .
on the 24 th , 26 zhejiang tourists and a team leader went to thailand under the organization of the hangzhou china travel agency .
li hui , deputy general manager of the hangzhou china travel agency , said that on the morning of the 27 th , 26 tourists left puji island with the tour guide , and went to the panyu island for a tour , and arrived at the destination at about 10 : 00 a.m . local time .
after tourists landed on the shore , the sea water immediately rose , and people mistakenly thought that it was a rising tide , so they did not care about it .
tourist guide cai weiwei , after discovering that the sea water was strong , reminded people to quickly run toward the hotel on the shore to avoid danger .
when everyone ran into the hotel hall , the sea water had already risen to the entrance of the hotel .
the hotel has three layers , and the surging waves have been flooded to the second floor , and everyone can only stay in the top of the building , and the sea water has not continued to rise .
of the 26 tourists , 19 are employees of the china united engineering company .
the reporter learned from the company that after the tsunamis , the trapped staff members and workers made phone calls to the company for help , and the company immediately requested emergency rescue through the chinese ministry of foreign affairs .
on hearing the news , the chinese embassy in thailand took emergency measures and sent personnel to the scene to deal with the incident . at that time , two people had lost contact .
it was not until the evening of the 26 th that the company contacted two staff members and workers who had followed other tourist groups to withdraw from puji island in advance , and one staff member who was slightly injured also left the panco island by the thai government 's rescue boat at the earliest possible time , and had been treated .
after the tsunami occurred , the local transportation department made all - out efforts to rescue the wounded .
at noon on the 27 th , they were safely transferred to puji island .
li hui said : at present , the tourism group is anxiously waiting for a return flight on thailand 's puji island . if the flight is arranged smoothly , " i hope they will return home tomorrow . "
