china banking regulatory commission to strengthen supervision over financial asset management companies
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 29 ( reporter wang weiping ) the china banking regulatory commission recently convened a work conference on strengthening the management and supervision of bad assets , and decided that the supervisory departments will " treat both the symptoms and the cause " and earnestly strengthen the supervision and management of financial assets management companies .
a responsible person of the china banking regulatory commission said on 29 june that the china banking regulatory commission will investigate and deal with the problems of violation of law and regulations in the management and handling of bad assets in accordance with the law , and will hand over the cases to the judicial organs for investigation and prosecution .
the results of handling major typical cases should be made public to the public and subject to social supervision through public exposure .
in the near future , the china banking regulatory commission will focus on improving and strengthening the supervisory mechanism for financial asset management companies in four aspects :
first , it is necessary to speed up the building of relevant laws and regulations of financial - assets management companies .
it is necessary to draw up a unified plan for the building of the laws and regulations of the financial - assets management companies , and resolve the current problems of imperfect laws and regulations of the financial - assets management companies .
the china banking regulatory commission will draft and promulgate as soon as possible the " guidelines for the work of handling the bad assets of financial - assets management companies , " the " procedures for the disclosure of information of financial - assets management companies , " and the " procedures for the punishment of illegal and irregular behavior of financial - assets management companies . "
second , it is necessary to improve the corporate management mechanism of financial - assets management companies , and resolve the problems of short - term behavior and moral risks in the operation of financial - assets management companies in terms of system , mechanism , and management .
third , it is necessary to strengthen and improve the supervision and management of financial - assets management companies .
relevant supervisory departments of the financial - assets management companies should divide the work and cooperate with one another , conscientiously perform their supervisory duties , form a joint force for supervision and management , and improve their supervisory efficiency .
fourth , it is necessary to continue to do a good job in the investigation and study of relevant policies and promote the improvement of the external environment for the disposal of assets , including the market environment , the legal and policy environment , and the construction of the market infrastructure for the exchange of bad assets .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) hong kong and macao residents applying to set up individual industrial and commercial households in shanghai to enjoy " green passage "
xinhua news agency , shanghai , december 30 ( reporter yu lihong ) as of january 1 , 2005 , hong kong and macao residents applying for the establishment of individual industrial and commercial households in shanghai will not need to be approved by foreign - funded departments . the applicants can directly download the registration form from the industrial and commercial website , and the 20 industrial and commercial sub-bureaus in the city will set up a " green channel " to receive applications .
this reporter has learned from the shanghai municipal administration of industry and commerce that the procedures for hong kong and macao residents to apply for the establishment of individual industrial and commercial households in shanghai are not complicated , and the materials that need to be submitted include the " application for the establishment of a registration of individual industrial and commercial households ( hong kong and macao residents ) " signed by the applicant , the identity documents and identity documents of the applicant , and other documents submitted by the state laws and regulations .
beginning 1 january 2005 , the shanghai industrial and commercial department will set up a special window and " green passage " at 20 sub-bureaus in the city to provide a one - stop service for hong kong and macao residents to apply for the registration of individual industrial and commercial households .
in addition , the shanghai industrial and commercial department has also set up a window on the official website ( www . sb . gov . cn ) for hong kong and macao residents to apply for the registration of individual industrial and commercial households in the mainland , and the applicant can directly download it .
the applicant can also find out the relevant information through online consultation , and the shanghai industrial and commercial website will give a reply within two working days to any questions concerning hong kong and macao residents applying for the registration of individual industrial and commercial households in shanghai .
it has been learned that the scope of operation permitted by hong kong and macao residents to apply for the registration of individual industrial and commercial households in shanghai is : the retail ( excluding tobacco retail ) , restaurants , residents ' services , and other service industries , such as hair and beauty care services , washing services , household electrical appliances repair , and other daily necessities , but they do not include the licensed operation .
at the same time , the composition of individual industrial and commercial households in hong kong and macao is limited to individual operations , with no more than eight employees and no more than 300 square meters of business space .
( international ) yugansk 's assets at auction will not be included in russian natural gas industry shareholding company
xinhua news agency report of december 30 th from moscow ( by staff reporter song shiyi ) - russian president 's office director and chairman of the russian natural gas industry company , medell , said to the media on the 30 th that the russian natural gas industry company will merge with the russian oil company as scheduled in january next year , but the assets of the russian oil company 's largest subsidiary , yugansk , will not be included in the assets of the russian natural gas industry company .
according to another report , russian minister of industry and energy khristenko said on the same day that the assets of yugansk , which were sold at the auction , would not be included in the assets of the russian natural gas industry company . this is mainly because the state is already the main shareholder of the russian oil and natural gas industry corporation , and the state does not want to increase its shares outside the controlling share .
he said yugansk 's assets would be separated alone and transferred to a wholly state - owned company .
on the 19 th of this month , the russian federation property fund held a public auction of the 76.79 percent stake of yugansk , the largest subsidiary of yukos oil company , and the newly formed bekal financial group won the bid at a price of 9.35 billion us dollars .
on the 22 nd , the state - owned russian oil company announced the acquisition of bekal financial group , which won the stake in yugansk , as a new shareholder of yugansk .
analysts believe that an important reason for russia 's clever operation in the auction of yugansk 's assets is that it is in a dominant position in relevant legal disputes .
in september this year , russian president putin approved the merger of the russian natural gas industry corporation .
the company , founded in february 1993 , is the largest natural gas company in the world .
the company holds 65 percent of russia 's natural gas reserves .
last year , the company 's natural gas output accounted for 93 percent of russia 's total output and 20 percent of the world 's total .
( earthquake ) tsunami hits indian state of tamil eelam
xinhua news agency , qinzhou , india , december 31 ( reporter jiang yaoping ) - the fishery industry in the state of tamil eelam in the southeastern part of india is developed .
the state has a long coastline of more than 1,000 kilometers , with an annual export of 370,000 tons of seafood and a foreign exchange of 23 billion rupees ( 1 us dollar to 43 rupees ) to the local government .
however , a rare tsunami triggered by a strong earthquake in the indian ocean on the 26 th caused unprecedented damage to local fishery production .
according to an authoritative source from the fishing industry in the capital of the state of tamil eelam , the sudden disaster had a huge impact on the state 's fishery production .
because there was no prior warning and precautionary measures , fishing vessels were all parked in the harbour .
as a result , more than 7,000 aircraft boats and more than 30,000 fireboats in the state were damaged to varying degrees , accounting for more than 80 percent of all vessels , and more than 30,000 fishing nets were damaged .
in an interview with xinhua on the 31 st , a responsible person of the chinai fishing federation said that even if the fishing boats were repaired , the fishermen did not dare to go to the sea in recent months , because they saw with their own eyes the storm and cruelty of the sea .
some people have lost their loved ones and their property has been damaged , and their psychological fear will stay for a considerable period of time .
according to estimates , the state 's fishery output in 2005 will be about 30 percent lower than that in 2004 .
during the tsunami disaster on the 26 th , most of the coastal fishing villages in the state of tamil eelam were hit and became the most serious disaster - stricken area in india .
up to the 30 th , more than 6,230 people have died in the state , most of whom are fishermen .
about 68,000 people in the state were affected by the tsunamis , and 85 percent of them were engaged in fishery production .
at present , the indian government is actively carrying out rescue work in an effort to restore local fishermen 's livelihood and fishery production as soon as possible .
shanghai airport bid farewell to the old year and greet the new in ice and snow
xinhua news agency , shanghai , january 1 ( feng yizhen and su jianwei ) - the staff of the shanghai airport bid farewell to the old year and greet the new in the snow and snow .
after two days of struggle against snow and snow , the staff of the shanghai airport group welcomed the last flight in 2004 at 2350 on the 31 st .
the operation of the m2566 flight from sydney to shanghai by the eastern airlines landed at the pudong airport in shanghai , and the transportation production of the shanghai civil aviation in 2004 has been completed .
in 2004 , the two major airports in shanghai took off and took off nearly 330,000 sorties , up 35 percent over the same period of last year , and the number of passengers transported by 36 million , up 45 percent over the same period of last year , with a net increase of 11.2 million people , and the volume of cargo handling exceeding 2.25 million tons , up nearly 40 percent over the same period last year , a net increase of 640,000 tons over the previous year .
in 2004 , the shanghai airport added another 16 cities for international scheduled flights , and the number of foreign airlines newly opened scheduled flights in shanghai reached five .
at present , there are 76 domestic cities and 86 international and regional cities , 11 domestic airlines and 38 international and regional airlines operating scheduled flights to shanghai .
in the last two days at the end of the year , the airport was closed for a time , the parking area was full of aircraft , and a large number of flights were delayed .
however , with the joint efforts of civil aviation staff , the last day at the end of the year , the air traffic was maintained smooth and the operational order was restored to normal .
wu nianzu , president of the airport group , who has been working with the airport staff , announced at midnight that the shanghai airport group has realized the fifth safety year , and this is also the 17 th safety year of the shanghai hongqiao airport .
wu nianzu said : in 2005 , the shanghai hongqiao airport will undergo a comprehensive renovation , the airport runway , the boarding process , and the appearance of the waiting building will be fully repaired , and the second runway of the pudong airport will be put into use . the first phase of the airport will be transformed , and the passenger handling capacity of the two major airports in shanghai is expected to reach 42 million passengers in 2005 .
famous chinese musicians perform new year concert in hangzhou
xinhua news agency report of january 2 from hangzhou ( by staff reporter qu chuan ) - the light and fast " song of spring " , the classic " blue danube " , and the chinese mainland premiere of the " salsea " and the " small violin recital " by schuster . on the evening of new year 's day , the hangzhou people listened to a new year concert performed by the global chinese star orchestra .
the music of the concert is all classic works in vienna , the capital of music .
the meticulous attitude of the artists brought about the success of the new year concert .
with 1,600 seats in the music hall , the audience will always be immersed in the music of world music .
the global chinese star orchestra , including the principal and deputy principal members of a number of well - known overseas bands , is well - known , such as the united states ' violin ensemble , the chief violinist of the berlin german symphony orchestra , and the principal violinist of the los angeles philharmonic orchestra , mr wang bin .
they represent the level of chinese classical music in europe .
this is the first visit to the mainland by the orchestra .
the orchestra made its first appearance at the hong kong handover ceremony in 1997 and was a great success , and its style of performance was both soft and soft , and its style was naturally smooth , and it was very strong and prudent , and did not lose the details .
water lan , artistic director of the singapore symphony orchestra , who is the conductor of the orchestra , said that although the musicians are distributed in various european , american , and asian countries and regions , and the schedule is tight , in order to ensure the quality of the performance , they have gathered in hangzhou ahead of time and conducted two days of rehearsal .
