xinhua news agency , london , january 2 , the " king of the car " shumae will reach the age of 36 on the 3 rd of this month . however , this one - class formula ( f1 ) , the oldest germans in active service , believes that age is not an obstacle to his advancement toward higher achievements .
during his 15 - year career in the 1 st century , schumacher took part in 212 sub - stations , 83 of which won the championship .
he also won the annual cycling championship seven times .
schumacher said on his personal website : " after taking part in the competition for so many years , i will surely leave many injuries on my body , but the injuries are not serious .
i feel that i am now in good health .
to be honest , i think i am much younger than 36 .
i often play golf with my colleagues , for example , allongso .
i am 10 years old than him , but people cannot see such a big difference between us at the stadium . "
many people believe that because of the long " victory " of schumacher , the competition has lost concern about the f1 , and it has turned out that there is no question of it .
when asked whether he was somewhat tired of the racing because of his lack of competitors , schumacher gave a very firm answer : " no , i am not tired at all , especially psychologically . "
i am still very enthusiastic about this sport . "
the new season 's f1 competition will start with the australian championship competition on march 6 .
looking forward to the upcoming 2005 season , schumacher is still full of confidence in victory .
he said : " like the previous season , i am full of thirst for victory .
in sports competitions , you cannot always be immersed in the achievements of the past . you should constantly meet the challenges , and i am very eager to accept the challenges . "
