xinhua news agency , haikou , january 3 ( reporter wang yingcheng ) this reporter learned from the hainan provincial people 's government that in 2005 , hainan province 's fixed assets investment will reach 34 billion yuan , so as to accelerate infrastructure construction and increase investment in key industries .
it is learned that in 2005 , hainan province invested 22.2 billion yuan in capital construction , 1.3 billion yuan in renovation and transformation , 5.5 billion yuan in real estate development , and 5 billion yuan in urban and rural collective and private investment .
at the same time , in 2005 , hainan will invest 10.5 billion yuan in 34 provinces ' key construction projects , raise the level of infrastructure , speed up the expansion of the meilan and phoenix airports , build two reservoirs in the second phase of the dalong and the daguang dam , expand the two docks at the haikou port and eight ports , build the haikou city expressway and the western expressway link , and start the construction of the fourth phase of the haikou power plant .
supporting the " three agricultural " development is one of the focal points of hainan province 's fixed assets investment in 2005 .
hainan will step up the work and support of the drought - fighting and disaster - relief organizations , increase the funds for the construction of wells and water - diversion facilities , strengthen the construction of agricultural infrastructure , speed up the construction of large water conservancy projects , exempt the agricultural tax , abolish the tax on animal husbandry , increase the subsidies for the peasants in the main grain - producing areas , support the processing of agricultural products and the leading agricultural enterprises , intensify the training of rural labor force , and organize peasants to work in the rural areas .
in 2005 , hainan province will continue to increase investment in public services and social undertakings .
