xinhua news agency , fuzhou , january 5 ( wang fanfan and li bingyuan ) - according to a relevant department of shishi city , fujian province , in 2004 , the per capita net income of peasants in this city reached 8038 yuan , an increase of 10% over the same period of last year , ranking first in various counties and cities in fujian province .
after the implementation of the tax reform in 2004 , the total annual burden on peasants in this city reached 722.72 million yuan , with a negative rate of 85.6 percent , and an average of 41.5 yuan per capita .
shi lion , " china 's leisure and clothing city , " has won the title of " 100 strong counties ( cities ) with basic competitiveness in the national county economy , and fujian province 's top 10 counties ( cities ) with economic strength .
since 2004 , the city has accelerated the process of modern agricultural construction , and marked results have been achieved in agricultural and rural work .
at present , shishi city has taken the lead in the whole province in providing public transportation to every village , providing water for every village , and providing cable television service to every village .
at present , the urbanization level of this city has reached 51 percent , ranking first in the province 's county - level city .
the city has also vigorously promoted the integration of the minimum living standards for urban and rural residents and the new type of medical insurance for all the people in rural areas .
the standard of low security for rural residents has been raised from an average of 100 yuan per month to 200 yuan equivalent to that of urban residents .
the new type of medical insurance for all the people in the rural areas , which each person needs to pay a medical insurance fee of 60 yuan per year , is only required to pay 10 yuan , and the rest are the financial burden of the cities and towns . at present , 106 thousand peasants enjoy this policy .
in 2004 , shishi city 's budget for agricultural aid was 20.2 million yuan , an increase of 10.38% over the same period last year .
through the free vocational and technical training of rural labor force , a total of 1,017 people were transferred to work in the whole year .
the city of shishi has also allocated 5 million yuan from the financial budget as a new start - up and reward fund for the transformation of old and new towns in the rural areas . at present , the number of old and new villages has reached 86 , accounting for 85 percent of the total number of administrative villages , and plans to complete the task of transforming old and new buildings in an all - round way in 2005 .
