( international ) south korea on trial broadcast of satellite digital multimedia broadcasting
xinhua news agency , seoul , january 10 ( reporter zhang jinfang ) the successful trial broadcast of south korea 's satellite digital multimedia broadcasting on the 10th marked the beginning of the era of digital multimedia broadcasting in south korea .
the so - called satellite digital multimedia broadcasting refers to the form of using satellites to broadcast multimedia broadcasting and television programs , and viewers can receive program signals in mobile terminals such as mobile phones .
on the morning of the 10th , the tband media company under the k - k communications company opened a total of nine channels for satellite digital multimedia broadcasting , including three television programs , including news , music , and television dramas , and six music programs , including the latest popular songs , old songs , and jazz music .
on the same day , the sk communications company introduced the first batch of 250 mobile phones capable of receiving satellite digital multimedia broadcasting , and some of the viewers received the satellite digital multimedia broadcasting programs with these mobile phones .
it has been learned that the rok government has listed satellite digital multimedia broadcasting as a key scientific and technological project , and has actively supported enterprises in developing satellite digital multimedia broadcasting technology and its products .
in april 2004 , the rok national assembly passed a revised " broadcasting law " to allow satellite digital multimedia broadcasting .
at the end of 2003 , the republic of korea 's salk communications company and japanese enterprises jointly set up a tband media company to prepare for the establishment of a satellite digital multimedia broadcasting station .
samsung electronics company and nmg electronics company have successfully developed mobile phones for receiving satellite digital multimedia broadcasting .
relevant departments in south korea have decided that the satellite digital multimedia broadcasting will first be broadcast on a trial basis for four months , starting from may this year .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) research institutes predict that hong kong 's economy will grow by about 6% in 2005
xinhua news agency , hong kong , january 11 ( reporter su xiao ) the asia - pacific economic cooperation research center of the university of hong kong said on the 11 th that the global economic environment is still optimistic this year , and it is estimated that hong kong 's economy will grow by about 6% this year , and will grow by 4.4% in the first quarter of this year .
at a news conference on " hong kong 's macroeconomic forecasts , " wang yu - chi , director of the hong kong greater asia - pacific economic cooperation research center , said that although the interest rate is expected to rise this year , the economic growth of hong kong 's major trade partners is slow , and the us and mainland china 's economy will grow by 3.6 percent and 8.5 percent respectively , the global economic environment in 2005 is still optimistic .
he said that the center forecasts that hong kong 's economy will maintain a growth rate of about 6% in 2005 , and consumer prices will rise by 3% at the end of the year .
the adjustment of the labour market is still slow , and the unemployment rate will be slightly reduced to around 6.3 per cent at the end of the year .
the instability caused by fluctuations in global oil prices remains the major uncertainties in hong kong 's economy .
the deputy director of the research centre , mr shao qizhen , said that the momentum of economic growth in the first quarter of this year would slow down , the gdp would grow by 4.4 percent , and the slowdown in growth reflected the gradual decline in hong kong 's external demand , as a result of the slower economic growth of hong kong 's major trading partners .
according to the report , hong kong 's real gdp in 2004 will have a strong growth of 8% , with the average price level only slightly down by 0.5% , and deflation also disappeared in the third quarter of last year .
zhou yiqing , chairman of the preparatory committee of the hong kong university 's " hong kong observation economic forecast , " said that the strong growth of hong kong 's economy in 2004 mainly reflects the strong economic foundation of hong kong , the strong competitiveness of the foreign trade market , and the benefits of the strong growth of the global economy and the rapid growth of the mainland 's market economy last year , and the end of the deflation problem has enabled the business people to enjoy more mobile cash .
( sino - foreign exchanges ) shanghai world expo becomes new link of sino - portuguese cooperation
xinhua news agency , shanghai , january 14 ( reporter wu yu and zhou jierong ) - visiting portuguese president sampaio attended the signing ceremony of the memorandum of cooperation between shanghai and portugal on world expo affairs on the evening of the 14 th .
this indicates that the 2010 world expo in shanghai is becoming a new link of cooperation between china and portugal .
sampaio said portugal has great enthusiasm and interest in fully participating in the organization of the shanghai world expo , and believes that with the efforts and wisdom of the chinese people , the shanghai world expo will be a success in five and a half years .
he stressed that as a rapidly developing international metropolis , shanghai is playing an increasingly important role in enhancing mutual understanding among the people of the whole world and the cause of world peace , and the shanghai world expo will surely become an important event .
sampaio expressed great hope for the cooperation between portugal and china in world expo affairs .
he said : at present , it is an important period for the development of the relations between portugal and china . it is hoped that with the shanghai world expo as a link , the good relations between the two countries will be further expanded from the political field to the economic , trade , cultural , tourism , and educational fields , and further promote the comprehensive development of the relations between the eu and china .
according to presentations , the cooperation between shanghai and portugal in world expo affairs involves the planning of the park , the design of the exhibition hall , the follow - up use of the exhibition equipment , and the various business plans , project management , operational procedures , and themes involved in the operation of the world expo , the media , the training of human resources , the security system , and the control and ticketing strategy .
prior to the signing of the mou , shanghai mayor han zheng met with president sampaio and his party .
( international ) you xianke calls for withdrawal of supporters from kiev
xinhua news agency , kiev , january 14 , the two presidential candidates in ukraine took a tit - for - tat action on the same day , according to media reports here today .
former prime minister yjinkovic filed a lawsuit with the supreme court demanding the overthrowing of the results of the presidential election announced by the central election commission , while the opposition leader , vitorino , asked his supporters to withdraw from the tents set up in the center of kiev for the protest activities .
a representative of the federation of southeast asian nations ( unkovic ) , shuvich , submitted 621 volumes of written materials and 233 sets of audio - video tapes to the supreme court as evidence .
he emphatically pointed out that if the court makes an unjust ruling , the supporters of aceh will launch a large - scale protest throughout the country .
at the same time , you xianke and his assistants discussed the issue of forming a new government .
he issued a statement on his campaign website , saying that he would establish a new government that is widely representative , and " invited all political forces inside and outside the parliament that are willing to build a country to join the cabinet . "
analysts pointed out that the move of the former soviet union in demanding the withdrawal of supporters from the center of kiev shows that he has confirmed that the supreme court will reject the appeal of the former yugoslavia , and that there is no obstacle to his election .
however , he did not set a specific time limit for the removal .
according to the official results of the second round of the presidential election released by the ukrainian central election commission on the evening of 10 april , 51.99 percent of the votes in the first round of voting were counted , and 44.20 percent of the votes were counted .
chinese government issues " regulations on protection of railway transportation safety "
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 15 , state council premier wen jiabao recently signed state council decree no. 430 to promulgate the " regulations on the protection of railway transportation safety . "
the " regulations " are divided into 103 articles and will come into force on 1 april 2005 .
the " regulations " are formulated in accordance with the " prc railway law " and the " prc law on safe production " in order to strengthen the management of railway transportation safety , ensure the safety and smooth flow of railway transportation , and protect personal safety , property safety , and other legitimate rights and interests .
the " regulations " point out that the departments in charge of railways under the state council are responsible for supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation throughout the country .
the railway management organization set up by the state council 's railway management department is responsible for supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation in the region .
the " regulations " said that the local people 's governments at all levels and the people 's governments at and above the county level in the areas along the railway should do a good job in the work related to the safety of railway transportation in accordance with their respective responsibilities , strengthen education on the safety of railway transportation , implement the responsibility system for the protection of roads , prevent and stop acts that endanger the safety of railway transportation , and coordinate and handle matters related to the safety of railway transportation .
the " regulations " point out that public security organs should , in accordance with their duties , divide the work , maintain public order at railway stations , trains , and other railway sites , and maintain law and order along the railway lines .
railway transportation enterprises should strengthen the management of railway transportation safety , establish and improve a safe production management system , set up safety management organs , and ensure the investment of funds needed for railway transportation safety .
railway transportation personnel should adhere to their posts , work according to procedures , fulfill their duties , and ensure transportation safety .
( international ) overseas chinese in japan support china 's anti - secession law
xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 18 ( reporter le shaoyan ) the china council for promoting peace held a meeting in the zhongshan memorial hall in yokohama a few days ago , expressing firm support for the chinese government 's formulation of the anti - secession law and its efforts to promote the great cause of the reunification of the motherland .
the meeting held that " taiwan independence " is the greatest harm to the interests of taiwan compatriots and is the greatest threat to the situation in the taiwan strait .
the formulation of the anti - secession law is conducive to cracking down on taiwan independence forces and their separatist activities , to peace and stability in the taiwan strait , and to the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation . fundamentally speaking , it is aimed at protecting the vital interests of the taiwan compatriots , and is a legal guarantee for realizing the aspirations of the broad masses of taiwan compatriots for peace , stability , and development .
the meeting also adopted a statement expressing firm support for the government 's formulation of an anti - secession law to safeguard china 's reunification .
the statement said : the extremely splittist activities carried out by the " taiwan independence " forces have fundamentally undermined the one - china principle and harmed the fundamental interests of the chinese nation .
it is the common will of overseas chinese and compatriots on both sides of the taiwan strait to stop the separatist acts of " taiwan independence " elements through legislation .
the statement held that the formulation of the anti - secession law fully reflects the great sincerity of the chinese government and people in upholding peaceful reunification and their firm determination to resolutely safeguard state sovereignty and territorial integrity , and has won popular support , and the broad masses of overseas chinese and ethnic chinese in japan fully support and resolutely support it .
the federation of overseas chinese and foreign nationals of chinese origin in japan , the association of overseas chinese in tokyo , and the association of people of taiwan province in japan also issued statements on the same day , expressing support for china 's formulation of an anti - secession law and resolutely safeguarding national reunification .
( international ) lima celebrates 470 th anniversary of founding of peru
xinhua news agency report of january 18 th from lima ( by staff reporter wang lu ) - the citizens of lima , the capital of peru , held large - scale and colorful cultural and entertainment activities in various parts of the city on the 18 th to solemnly celebrate the 470 th anniversary of the founding of the city .
public places such as parks and churches in lima city held various kinds of celebration activities organized by the municipal government and nongovernmental organizations on the same day , including the large - scale mass prayer meeting , the sale of national products , and the famous peruvian " infantry horse " performance .
lima , mayor of the city , said that the city , which has a long history , is developing in the direction of standardization and modernization , and he will put the improvement of the city 's economic environment and the improvement of social service projects in the first place .
on the evening of the 17 th , nearly 3,000 citizens watched a brilliant and colorful song and dance evening party held by the city government at the weapons square in the center . the five - colored lights were dressed in the ancient buildings around the square , and the famous song and dance artists performed ethnic songs and dances in different regions .
the city residents also watched fireworks display and celebrated the night together .
on january 18 , 1535 , spanish adventurer pizo came to the bank of the markus river to establish a lima city and set up a government house . he also said that this was to express his respect for the then spanish king juan carlos 5 and the king of the queen mary , and that lima was called the " king 's city . "
after peru became independent in 1821 , lima became a national political , economic , and cultural center .
at present , the city 's area has increased from 2.14 square kilometers in the early days of the founding of the city to more than 2,600 square kilometers , and the population has increased to about 8 million , accounting for about 31 percent of the country 's total population .
( international ) argentine vice president and senate president meet with li tieying
xinhua news agency , buenos aires , january 19 ( reporter cao yu and shen an ) when meeting with li tieying , vice chairman of the standing committee of the national people 's congress [ npc ] of china , and a delegation of the chinese people 's congress [ npc ] led by li tieying at the government palace on the 19 th , argentine vice president and president of the senate , expressed the hope to further strengthen the friendly and cooperative relations between argentina and china in various fields .
xiao li said : in 2004 , the two countries exchanged visits by top leaders , established a strategic partnership , signed a series of friendly and cooperative agreements , and continued to develop friendly relations between the two countries .
at present , the relations between the two countries are in the best period in history , and it is hoped that the two sides will further strengthen all - round cooperation in the future , especially exchanges between the argentine parliament and the chinese npc .
xiaoli said that argentina attaches great importance to developing strategic partnership with china and learn from china 's valuable experience in economic development .
argentina agrees with the one - china stand .
li tieying first conveyed chairman wu bangguo 's regards to vice president and senate president xiao li .
li tieying said : in 2004 , the exchange of visits between the argentine president and chinese president hu jintao and the decision to establish a strategic partnership between the two countries have entered a new stage in sino - argentine relations .
the chinese government attaches great importance to developing relations with latin american countries , including argentina .
li tieying said : the chinese government appreciates argentina 's adherence to the one - china stand .
li tieying and his entourage arrived in buenos aires on 18 april for a friendly visit to argentina at the invitation of the argentine national assembly .
he also met with argentine house of representatives speaker karmano .
the chinese npc delegation led by li tieying will also pay friendly visits to uruguay and brazil .
( international ) cis collective security treaty plans to strengthen military strength to deal with threats
xinhua news agency , moscow , january 20 , the secretary general of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) collective security treaty , bolzza , said on the 20th that the organization would strengthen its military strength to cope with the major threats facing the contemporary world , such as international terrorism , drug trafficking , illegal immigration , and organized crime .
speaking at an international symposium on the organization of the collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) held in moscow on the same day , bolzizza said that the joint forces of the organization , which are currently being established in central asia , will have a series of practical measures to ensure that the joint forces of russia and belarus in eastern europe and the experience of the russian and armenian troops in the caucasus .
he said : according to the joint military construction plan for the period from now to 2010 , the organization will establish a unified air defense , communications , and information investigation support system in central asia .
at the same time , we will also formulate a unified standard for the training of military personnel and establish relevant material and technological reserves .
bolzizza pointed out that the establishment of a rapid reaction force of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) collective security treaty is conducive to curbing the extremist forces in central asia , and that the force has demonstrated this strength in last year 's military exercise .
he stressed that the organization would not use troops in areas outside its member states .
the cis collective security treaty organization has six member states , namely , russia , armenia , kazakhstan , kyrgyzstan , tajikistan , and belarus .
its predecessor was the collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states signed by the six countries in 1992 .
in may 2002 , the council of the collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states decided to change the " collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states " into the " collective security treaty organization of the commonwealth of independent states " and set up a military management organization of the collective security treaty .
at the same time , beijing also promulgated seven safety management standards for " personnel - intensive " sites
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 24 ( reporter zhang shanmiao wentao ) the beijing municipal commercial administration bureau , the cultural bureau , and the yuanlin bureau jointly issued on the 24 th seven safety management regulations on " personnel - intensive places " such as shopping malls and parks .
lu hao , vice mayor of beijing , believes that the formulation and release of these seven safety management standards is a concrete embodiment of the standardization of beijing 's safety quality .
the " beijing municipality 's shopping malls and supermarkets safety management standards ( trial implementation ) , " " beijing municipality 's safety management standards ( trial implementation ) , " " beijing municipality 's internet service business sites safety management standards ( trial implementation ) , " and " beijing municipality 's park , scenic spots , and scenic spots safety management regulations ( trial implementation ) , " and other seven safety management regulations , such as the " beijing municipality 's regulations on the safety of the performing venues , " have also set strict standards for the
liu sheng , chief engineer of the beijing municipal garden forestry bureau , told this reporter that the seven " regulations " have for the first time studied and made explicit stipulations on the relationship between the operating area and the number of customers in the shopping malls , supermarkets , and cinemas and parks . for example , the " regulations on the safety management of beijing 's parks , scenic spots , and places of historical interest ( trial ) " clearly stipulate that the park management organs should be able to receive tourists in accordance with the " park design standards . "
the seven " regulations " will be implemented on a trial basis within two months before and after the spring festival , and will be formally implemented at the same time on 24 march 2005 .
